### 9.4.2 Semantic Zoom Levels

| Zoom Level | Time Visible | Cell Size | Content | Rendering |
|------------|--------------|-----------|---------|-----------|
| **Strategic** (0-4) | 10+ years | Year | Heatmap (PM density) | WebGL (deck.gl) |
| **Tactical-Wide** (4-8) | 2-3 years | Quarter | Compressed blocks | WebGL (deck.gl) |
| **Tactical** (8-12) | 3-12 months | Month/Week | Gantt bars + labels | HTML Canvas |
| **Operational** (12-16) | 1-3 months | Week | Cards with details | HTML Canvas |
| **Detail** (16-20) | 1-4 weeks | Day | Expanded cards | React DOM |

